gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 114, Magic 97
gameRecap.excerpt: Boston won its fifth consecutive game as they defeated the Magic, 114-97. Jaylen Brown led Boston with 31 points, five rebounds, and six assists as Jayson Tatum added 23 points and eight rebounds. Paolo Banchero led Orlando with 36 points (4 3PT) and 10 rebounds. The Celtics are now 14-0 at home, remaining the only undefeated team at home in the league, and improve to 20-5 as the Magic move to 16-9.
